'''大中东地区'''（{{lang-en|'''The Greater Middle East'''}}）是[[美国|美国]][[乔治·W·布什|乔治·W·布什政府]]于21世纪的前10年创建来描述[[穆斯林世界|穆斯林世界]]附近的国家，尤其是[[伊朗|伊朗]]、[[土耳其|土耳其]]、[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]和[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]的[[政治地理学|政治地理学]]名词。<ref name=haeri>{{Cite news|url=http://www.atimes.com/atimes/Middle_East/FC04Ak06.html|accessdate=2008-08-21|title=Concocting a 'Greater Middle East' brew|work=[[Asia_Times|Asia Times]]|date=2004-03-03|first=Safa|last=Haeri|archive-date=2013-08-19|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6IzIZXPxI?url=http://www.atimes.com/atimes/Middle_East/FC04Ak06.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>Ottaway, Marina & Carothers, Thomas (2004-03-29), [http://www.carnegieendowment.org/publications/index.cfm?fa=view&id=1480 The Greater Middle East Initiative: Off to a  False Start] {{Wayback|url=http://www.carnegieendowment.org/publications/index.cfm?fa=view&id=1480 |date=20180708030632 }}, Policy Brief, ''Carnegie Endowment for International Peace'', 29, Pages 1-7</ref>一些位于[[南高加索|南高加索]]和[[中亚|中亚]]的国家有时也会包括进去。一些演说家会用此名词来形容全部以伊斯兰教（穆斯林）为主的国家，但这个说法不具有普遍性。<ref>[[Dimitri_Kitsikis|Dimitri Kitsikis]], «Les frontières de sang - Géopolitique d'un Proche-Orient à venir»,''Diplomatie'', no.24, janvier-février 2007</ref>大中东地区有时也会称为'''新中东地区'''（{{lang-en|'''The New Middle East'''}}）或'''大中东计划'''（{{lang-en|'''The Greater Middle East Project'''}}）<ref name="urukut">{{Cite web|url=http://www.globalresearch.ca/index.php?context=viewArticle&code=NAZ20061116&articleId=3882|accessdate=2008-08-21|title=Plans for Redrawing the Middle East: The Project for a "New Middle East"|date=2006-11-18|first=Mahdi Darius|last=Nazemroaya|work=Global Research|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226062413/https://www.globalresearch.ca/plans-for-redrawing-the-middle-east-the-project-for-a-new-middle-east/3882|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sakarya.edu.tr/en/?nid=237 |title=“Great Middle East Project” Conference by Prof. Dr. Mahir Kaynak and Ast.Prof. Dr. Emin Gürses in SAU |access-date=2016-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180122071832/http://www.sakarya.edu.tr/en/?nid=237 |archive-date=2018-01-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.emep.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=155:-the-greater-middle-east-project-the-new-name-for-occupation-and-re-division&catid=47:articles&Itemid=98 |title=Turkish Emek Political Parties |accessdate=2016-07-10 |archive-date=2014-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502230715/http://www.emep.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=155:-the-greater-middle-east-project-the-new-name-for-occupation-and-re-division&catid=47:articles&Itemid=98 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

这个拓展名词来自美国政府[[第30届八国集团首脑会议|2004年的G8峰会]]的准备工作，作为彻底改变[[西方世界|西方世界]]应对中东问题方式的提案的一部分。<ref name=Perthes>Perthes, V., 2004, [http://www.mepc.org/journal_vol11/0409_perthes.asp America's "Greater Middle East" and Europe: Key Issues for Dialogue] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mepc.org/journal_vol11/0409_perthes.asp |date=20081115112943 }}, ''[[Middle_East_Policy|Middle East Policy]]'', Volume XI, No.3, Pages 85-97.</ref>

